OL,3,CPublic sector gender pay gap down 43%
OL,4,Cin three years, says report
OL,6,FThe average pay gap between men and
OL,7,Fwomen working in Jersey's public
OL,8,Fsector has dropped by 43% in the last
OL,9,Fthree years.
OL,11,FNew Government data shows the median
OL,12,Fdifference in hourly wages was 8.6% in
OL,13,F2025 compared to 15% in 2022.
OL,15,FHowever, that still means that women
OL,16,Fworking in the public sector earn only
OL,17,F92.2p for every #1 earned by a man.
