OL,3,CPublic sector gender pay gap down 43%
OL,4,Cin three years, says report
OL,6,FThe report, published today, also
OL,7,Ffound that a higher proportion of
OL,8,Fwomen work in part-time or reduced
OL,9,Fhour jobs due to caring
OL,10,Fresponsibilities.
OL,12,FIt also shows that more than three
OL,13,Fquarters of those working for Jersey's
OL,14,FEducation and Health departments were
OL,15,Fwomen but that most flexible roles,
OL,16,Fincluding teaching assistants, are
OL,17,Fevaluated at lower grades and attract
OL,18,Fmainly women.
