OL,3,CPublic sector gender pay gap down 43%
OL,4,Cin three years, says report
OL,6,FAlmost half of all public service
OL,7,Fstaff work in Education or Health with
OL,8,Fwomen making up 64.3% of the workforce.
OL,10,FDespite the narrowing gap, certain
OL,11,Fpublic sector jobs are still largely
OL,12,Fdominated by one gender.
OL,14,F89.9% of teaching assistants are women
OL,15,Fwith 80.9% of nurses and midwives
OL,16,Fbeing female.
