OL,3,CPublic sector gender pay gap down 43%
OL,4,Cin three years, says report
OL,6,FAt the other end of the spectrum, 97%
OL,7,Fof Jersey Fire and Rescue Service
OL,8,Femployees are male, with more than two
OL,9,Fthirds of those working for the police
OL,10,Falso being men.
OL,12,FReflecting on the report's findings,
OL,13,FDeputy Malcolm Ferey, Vice Chair of
OL,14,Fthe States Employment Board, said:
OL,15,F"This does not mean men and women are
OL,16,Fpaid differently in the public service
OL,17,Ffor doing the same job. We pay all
OL,18,Fstaff equally for the same roles
OL,19,Fwithin any specified pay group.
