OL,3,CPublic sector gender pay gap down 43%
OL,4,Cin three years, says report
OL,6,F"It is, however, possible to have a
OL,7,Fpay gap and to still pay people fairly
OL,8,Fand this data helps us to see where,
OL,9,Fon average, differences exist and why.
OL,11,F"Any gap is partly driven by roles in
OL,12,Fwhich one gender or another are
OL,13,Ftraditionally attracted to.
OL,15,F"While I'm pleased that the pay gap
OL,16,Fhas nearly halved since 2022, we are
OL,17,Fnot complacent and want to build on
OL,18,Fthis progress to ensure we can
OL,19,Funderstand and act on this data.
